// SCRIPTED // first council meeting
Dialog Mission Statement This is the dialog for Zhar Lestin, the Jedi trainer.
The first dialog is the initial Jedi Council meeting the player has just after he lands on Dantooine. The second dialog is Zhar assigning and testing the first test, and assigning the second. The third dialog is susequent conversations before the player has cleansed the grove. The fourth dialog is the first time after the player saved Juhani. The fifth dialog is the first time after the player killed Juhani. The sixth dialog is him assigning the third test. The seventh dialog is subsequent times before the player returns with a crystal. The eighth dialog is when the player returns with a crystal. The ninth dialog is once the player's lightsaber has been constructed. The tenth dialog is once the player has shown basic proficiency with the lightsaber. The eleventh dialog is after the player has defeated the shielded droid. The twelfth dialog is if the player failed to defeat Zhar. The thirteenth dialog is once the player has defeated Zhar. The fourteenth dialog is subsequent conversations.
Exit points in conversation:
Exit stream 1: The lines are spoken and the conversation ends. The player's responses do not affect the conversation. If the player shows arrogance, there is the possibility of a minor dark side hit. DAN_JEDI_PLOT is set to 1 to show that the player is being considered for Jedi training.
Exit stream 2: Zhar gives a quest based on what test the player needs to take. The player can also choose to exit the conversation. If the player passes the first test, DAN_PLOT_JEDI is set to 3 to show that the player has passed the first test. If he gives the second test, DAN_JUHANIQ_DONE is set to TRUE to show that the quest has been given, and if the player has already killed Juhani, DAN_JEDI_PLOT is set to 4 to show that the grove has been cleansed.
Exit stream 3: The line is spoken and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 4: The lines are spoken and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 5: The lines are spoken and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 6: The lines are spoken and the conversation ends. If the player accepts, DAN_ZHARL_DONE is set to TRUE to show that the player has been told to find the lightsaber crystals.
Exit stream 7: The line is spoken and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 8: All stream and at the construction of the lightsabe, but if the character is unrepentant he can suffer a minor dark side hit.
Exit stream 9: The line is said and the conversation ends. DAN_JEDI_PLOT is set to 6 to show that the player has constructed his lightsaber.
Exit stream 10: The lines are said and the player can either initiate combat or leave. DAN_ZHARH_DONE is set to TRUE to show that the player has shown basic poficiency.
Exit stream 11: The lines are said and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 12: The lines are said and the conversation ends.
Exit stream 13: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_JEDI_PLOT is set to 7 to show that the player has become a Padawan.
Exit stream 14: The lines are said and the conversation ends.
Only plays when the player first comes out of the training cutscene, never again.
